headline: Top 20 Companies Recognized in Labrador Transparency’s 2025 U.S. Transparency Awards
summary: ATLANTA, September 16, 2025--Lowe’s Companies, Dow, American Express, ConocoPhillips, and AIG secured top honors in the 2025 U.S. Transparency Awards announced today by Labrador Transparency, a leading global communications firm specializing in transparent corporate disclosure documents.
